{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1a326d6945","title":"致林彪等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b6c255d690","index":0,"year":1936,"month":4,"day":15,"articleId":"1a326d6945"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"641ad80260","type":"paragraph","text":"致林彪等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"1a326d6945"},{"id":"835882cfec","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年4月15日）林、是，张，陈、杨：一、一师占领清水关东岸，至诚等已渡过河东。二、红一军团伤员及全部现立即开始西渡。三、冯文彬等二十三日才能到清水关西渡，一师在清水关东岸一带待命，准备二十三日行动。四、一切东渡人员、部队机关、器材文件，统由杨至诚、宋裕和（军委四局副局长）率领随一师行动","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"1a326d6945"},{"id":"22acb4930b","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"1a326d6945"},{"id":"e46b1e7158","type":"paragraph","text":"十五日二十时[]这是毛泽东和红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀给第一方面军第一军团军团长林规、政治委员最荣聘，红军第一方西军副参谋长兼军委后方办事处","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"1a326d6945"}],"page":{"id":"1e57de4cbd","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"1a326d6945","start":388,"end":388}}}},"__N_SSG":true}